С o m m e n t. The only species of the genus 
<taxonomicName id="4C79DCC1FF82FF99F3FDFE3EED6CFE55" box="[747,860,404,430]" class="Insecta" family="Braconidae" genus="Paralipsis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="394" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
